data.description: This stunning ranch home is in move in condition. New flooring, paint, baseboards and primary bathroom is totally remodeled. Living Room has a wood burning fireplace with insert. Kitchen was remodeled some years ago. Newer stainless steel appliances, huge kitchen nook for dining. Hall bath has new vanity, paint. Double paned windows, RV parking in rear yard with separate gate with sewer clean out. Well water for irrigation. Back yard is set up for entertaining with bar. Central air & heat. This home sits on a large flat corner lot with 2 car attached garage. There is a separate small building on side yard that can be an office, yoga studio, weight room. Sewer lateral has been done. Clear termite report. Close to schools, buses, shopping and freeways, a must see!!!!
